title: MyRepository
text:
This is a Quarto website to document this repository.
Quarto is multiformat document generator that can be used as a static website generator. It is more powerful that a blog-oriented platform such as Jekyll, but less than documentation-oriented tools like Sphinx or Docusaurus. It is build on Pandoc and accepts multiple flavours of markdown.
To learn more about Quarto websites visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.
